node.text:
“The name is Captain Carter!” 🇬🇧 So excited for my new Peggy Carter cosplay from What If…! It’s such a beautiful design ….Although the fact that the Union Jack is asymmetrical made my perfectionist brain break 😂 The breastplate is definitely my favorite part - it is heat formed worbla with foam on top. Also I love the little leather pouches I made. They’re so cute!
*
*
Gorgeous 📸 set by @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
*
Cosplay pieces made or modified by me!
Peggy wig from the talented @timeaftertimedesigns ❤️
*
*
#captaincarter #captainbritain #peggycarter #whatif #disneyplus #hayleyatwell ##captainamerica #cosplay #marvel #worbla #foam

node.text:
I’m so incredibly honored that  @paramountpics hired me to recreate Scarlett’s incredible armored look for the upcoming @SnakeEyesMovie ! GI Joe was one of my favorite cartoons as a kid - I even made a Baroness as an adult so completing a new Scarlett was a dream come true! I just hope I did her justice!  She’s so much fun to wear ❤️
You can See Snake Eyes in theatres July 23rd. Get tickets now in @snakeeyesmovie ‘s Bio link! 
#SnakeEyes #ad

Some BTS of shooting my new Atom Eve cosplay with @geekstrong !! - featuring this creepy underpass (which had some AMAZING light 😂). This suit was head to toe puff painted and I also installed some heels. The puff painting took foreeeeverrrr because the design has teeny, tiny dots in shades of pink and purple! I’ll be posting photos shortly ❤️
*
*
Vid by @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
Suit design by @braekor and printed by Herostime

*
